---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Beaufort Laundry Fairy">
  <div class="pt-24 pb-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-primary hover:text-primary-dark transition-colors mb-8 text-sm font-medium">
      <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
      Back to Home
    </a>
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-heading mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-lg text-body space-y-6">
      <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> April 2026</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-heading mt-8">Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>When you use our booking form or contact us, we collect the information you provide, including your name, email address, phone number, and pickup address. This information is used solely to schedule and fulfill your laundry service.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-heading mt-8">How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use your personal information to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Schedule and coordinate laundry pickups and deliveries</li>
        <li>Send you invoices and payment links</li>
        <li>Communicate about your orders and respond to inquiries</li>
        <li>Improve our services</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-heading mt-8">Information Sharing</h2>
      <p>We do not sell, trade, or share your personal information with third parties, except as necessary to provide our services (e.g., payment processing through Stripe).</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-heading mt-8">Data Security</h2>
      <p>We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information. Payment processing is handled securely through Stripe, and we do not store credit card information.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-heading mt-8">Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:beaufortlaundryfairy@gmail.com" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-dark">beaufortlaundryfairy@gmail.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
